        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat(data): add bounded data run evidence",
        "body": "## Summary\n- Add `crabbox data` as a thin wrapper over `crabbox run` for repo-owned data workflows with required bounded manifests.\n- Validate `crabbox.data-run.v1` manifests locally, reject unsafe proof fields, and write bounded summaries under `.crabbox/data-runs/`.\n- Add provider-neutral delegated artifact retrieval plus Islo and W&B/CoreWeave single-file support for `--require-artifact` / `--download`, while keeping globs and unsupported delegated providers fail-closed.\n\n## Issues\nRefs https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/225\nRefs https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/227\nRefs https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/228\nRefs https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/229\nRefs https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/230\n\n## Test plan\n- `go test ./internal/cli ./internal/providers/islo ./internal/providers/wandb`\n- `go test ./...`\n- `scripts/check-docs.sh`\n\n## Live Islo proof\nShort-lived API key was created through `islo api-key create --expires 1`, used only via `CRABBOX_ISLO_API_KEY`, then deleted. Lease/sandbox IDs are redacted.\n\n```text\nISLO_LIVE_STATUS 0\nISLO_LIVE_PROOF_BEGIN\ndata policy source=declared-live-smoke sink=declared-live-smoke egress=provider-default promotion=manual enforcement=declared-only\nleased <redacted> slug=<redacted> provider=islo sandbox=<redacted>\nprovider=islo lease=<redacted> sandbox=<redacted>\nrequired artifact reports/data/manifest.json matched=1\nrequired artifact reports/data/empty.marker matched=1\ndownloaded .crabbox/data-runs/islo-live-proof/manifest.json bytes=189\nislo run summary sync_skipped=true command=425ms total=54.531s exit=0\n{\"provider\":\"islo\",\"leaseId\":\"<redacted>\",\"syncMs\":0,\"syncPhases\":[{\"name\":\"sync\",\"skipped\":true,\"reason\":\"--no-sync\"}],\"syncSkipped\":true,\"syncDelegated\":true,\"commandMs\":424,\"totalMs\":54531,\"exitCode\":0,\"label\":\"data:islo-live-proof\",\"artifacts\":[{\"kind\":\"delegated-download\",\"path\":\".crabbox/data-runs/islo-live-proof/manifest.json\",\"bytes\":189}]}\ndata run islo-live-proof manifest ok status=success inputs=0 outputs=1 summary=.crabbox/data-runs/islo-live-proof/summary.json\nISLO_LIVE_PROOF_END\n```\n\n## W&B/CoreWeave coverage\nLive W&B credentials were not present locally. The W&B delegated artifact path is covered with fake CoreWeave API tests, including required proof, local download, keep-on-failure, timing JSON, oversized-file rejection before retrieval, and zero-byte required artifact acceptance.",
